OL,3,CSouthern Water spent nearly #1bn since
OL,4,C2020 to 'turnaround' poor performance
OL,6,FThis year marks a 'final stretch' for
OL,7,Fits turnaround plan which was designed
OL,8,Fto deliver fast-tracked improvements
OL,9,Fto its performance, which in the
OL,10,Flatest review by the Environment
OL,11,FAgency 'required improvement'.
OL,13,FSouthern Water said the spending
OL,14,Fshowed its commitment to customers as
OL,15,Fit 'strives to live up to customer
OL,16,Fexpectations'.
OL,18,FBy this time next year, it expects
OL,19,Ftotal spending to pass #1.5bn, one of
OL,20,Fthe biggest spends in its history.
