OL,6,FThe company stressed that this money
OL,7,Fis in addition to its 'reactionary'
OL,8,Fwork, including current efforts to
OL,9,Freduce storm overflows into rivers and
OL,10,Fseas.
OL,12,FIn Hampshire, Southern Water has spent
OL,13,Fa total of #251 million so far. This
OL,14,Fincludes #97 million on its 'Water for
OL,15,FLife Hampshire' scheme, which includes
OL,16,Fplans for a new reservoir near Havant.
