OL,6,FOn the Isle of Wight, it spent #5.6
OL,7,Fmillion. This included #3m on
OL,8,Fimproving the resilience of supplies
OL,9,Fto the island to better 'withstand
OL,10,Fextreme weather events'.
OL,12,FWATCH: ITV Meridian's Matt Teale
OL,13,Fspeaks to Southern Water about their
OL,14,Fperformance.
OL,16,FIn Sussex, Southern invested #333
OL,17,Fmillion pounds into the network. #157m
OL,18,Fof this was used to 'better its
OL,19,Fwastewater treatment processes' at 37
OL,20,Fof its sites and reduce the impact to
OL,21,Fthe environment.
