OL,6,FIn Kent, #276 million was allocated to
OL,7,Fimprove its performance. #30m of this
OL,8,Fwas used to increase storm water
OL,9,Fstorage at 16 sites to reduce
OL,10,Foverflows into the sea.
OL,12,FJohn Penicud, Southern Water's
OL,13,FDirector for Wastewater Operations,
OL,14,Fsaid: "As we enter an absolutely
OL,15,Fcrucial year for Southern Water and
OL,16,Fthe wider water industry, it is right
OL,17,Fthat we are open with our customers
OL,18,Fabout what we are spending on
OL,19,Fimproving our performance and where
OL,20,Fthe money is going.
