OL,6,F"Contrary to some claims aired in the
OL,7,Fmedia and among the public, I'd like
OL,8,Fto reassure you that we are spending
OL,9,Four bill payers' and our shareholders'
OL,10,Fmoney in an ambitious, targeted and
OL,11,Fevidence-based way to fix the issues
OL,12,Fwe know we face.
OL,14,F"These figures on planned
OL,15,Finfrastructure projects demonstrate
OL,16,Fthat very clearly, and we will keep
OL,17,Fpushing ahead to achieve the results
OL,18,Feveryone wants to see."
